3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper discusses the training of a neural network model, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of neural networks and simulations to train an end-to-end navigation system is a common problem in the field of artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with the problem of transferring a model from simulations to the real world, which is a key problem in systems and control.
